  • CNS prophylaxis high-risk (CNS-IPI ≥ 4, testicular, breast, double-hit, kidney/adrenal);
  • Relapsed/refractory: CAR-T (axi-cel, liso-cel — ZUMA-7, TRANSFORM moved CAR-T to 2nd line) > auto-HCT;
  • Other: tafasitamab + lenalidomide, lonca-T, glofitamab/epcoritamab (bispecific), pola;

(9) IPI / NCCN-IPI risk;

(10) PMBCL distinct entity;

