  • L-glutamine (Endari);
  • Crizanlizumab (anti-P-selectin) — re-evaluated;
  • Voxelotor (HbS polymerization inhibitor) — withdrawn 2024 globally due to mortality signal;
  • Chronic transfusion (stroke prevention/secondary, recurrent ACS);
  • Curative: HLA-matched allo-HCT (children + selected adults); gene therapy — Lyfgenia (lovotibeglogene autotemcel) + Casgevy (exa-cel — CRISPR BCL11A — first FDA-approved CRISPR therapy 2023);

