DIC: systemic activation coag → consumption + bleeding + thrombosis. PT/PTT↑ + fibrinogen↓ + D-dimer↑↑ + plt↓ + schistocytes. ISTH score. Triggers: sepsis, APL, OB, trauma. Tx: treat cause + supportive (FFP/cryo/platelets for bleeding; LMWH for thrombotic). APL — ATRA immediate.

